示的内容系公司利用休息时间进行奶粉推广，并有公司管理人员点赞，应认定为加班。因此，小杨提交的加班时间明细表与加班微信截图的时间基本能对应，法院认定加班事实存在。法院认为，用人单位违法解除劳动关系的，应向劳动者支付赔偿金32411元，加班费18135.2元。 （参考来源：领导点赞下属加班的朋友圈！公司赔了1.8万！）"},"attached_info":"CkEI2+u0iNT88/hyEAMaCTExMjI5MTAwMCCT/uS6BjAAOKwBQBByCjY1NzE4NDU2OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"39 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-005fc36b8d815710ad441cd439cc95c5_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"17_1734353430.468139","card_id":"Q_6133109612","target":{"id":6133109612,"title":"哲学中主观与客观相统一是什么意思？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6133109612","type":"question","created":1733472880,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[478,116253,2095907,2267352,3529918],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI2+u0iNT88/hyEAMaCTExMjIwMzQ4NiDw5Mq6BjAAOD1AEXIKNjEzMzEwOTYxMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"38 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dec9c58bb7fd8423e1372822f2a3e93e_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1734353430.468590","card_id":"Q_6482143837","target":{"id":6482143837,"title":"对于即将毕业的国内本科生来说，出国打工是一个好的出路吗?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/6482143837","type":"question","created":1733818867,"answer_count":40,"follower_count":83,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3789,4287,8623,115918,1454596],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"结合目前国内大环境而言，相比于国内读研、考公考编，选择出国打工是否更划算？ 出国打工指直接去国外就职，或者以能留在国外就职为目标的短期留学（比如读语言学校等）"},"attached_info":"CkAI2+u0iNT88/hyEAMaCTExMjI3Mjk2MSDz89+6BjAAOFNAEnIKNjQ4MjE0MzgzN3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJ